# 🚆 ATTCS — AI Train Traffic Control System
## Complete Project Analysis

---

## 1. Project Overview

**ATTCS** is a **real-time AI-powered train traffic control simulation** built as a monolithic Java Spring Boot application with a rich single-page frontend. It simulates a railway network across **12 Indian cities** with **24 active trains**, **48 signals**, and **18 route segments**, all managed by four AI engines running natively in Java.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This was originally a Python + Java microservice architecture. All AI logic has been **migrated to pure Java**, making it a self-contained, single-process application.

