## 7. AI Algorithms Summary

| AI Engine | Algorithm | Complexity | Key Technique |
|-----------|----------|------------|---------------|
| **TrafficAI** | DFS Cycle Detection | O(V+E) | Wait-for graph → cycle = deadlock → reroute lowest-priority train |
| **AiOptimizer** | BFS Pathfinding | O(V!) worst | Multi-objective scoring (time/energy/capacity/conflict) |
| **AiPredictor** | Probabilistic Scoring | O(1) | Station risk factors × time-of-day multiplier + Gaussian noise |
| **AiDispatcher** | Priority Queue | O(n log n) | Sort by priority (high→low), status weighted by priority tier |
| **AiRescheduler** | Heuristic | O(n) | Pre-defined rescheduling scenarios with dynamic stats |

