## 8. Key Design Patterns

| Pattern | Where Used |
|---------|-----------|
| **MVC** | Controllers → Services → Repositories |
| **Facade** | `AiProxyService` wraps all 4 AI engines |
| **Repository** | Spring Data JPA auto-implemented repositories |
| **Scheduler** | `@Scheduled` for real-time train/signal simulation |
| **Graceful Degradation** | Frontend has local fallback data when API is unreachable |
| **Builder-like Init** | `@PostConstruct` methods build initial state |

